<subSubSection id="C3326E8AFFF1C1077FD7FAC1FE95F0BE" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" type="description">
<subSubSection id="C3326E8AFFF1C1077FD7FAC1FD98F04A" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B973D01FFF1C1077FD7FAC1FD98F04A" blockId="1.[136,1452,1395,1563]" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">
Five species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFF1C1077E67FAC1FE32F3DD" authorityName="Schimper" authorityYear="1851" box="[312,427,1395,1421]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Phyllodon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFF1C1077E67FAC1FE32F3DD" box="[312,427,1395,1421]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">Phyllodon</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have been known in 
<collectingCountry id="F33F7D91FFF1C1077DC3FAC1FD7AF3DD" box="[668,739,1395,1421]" name="China" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">China</collectingCountry>
: they are 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFF1C1077C10FAC6FC4AF3DD" authorityName="P. E. A. S. Camara" authorityYear="2010" baseAuthorityName="Dixon" box="[847,979,1395,1421]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="bilobatus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFF1C1077C10FAC6FC4AF3DD" box="[847,979,1395,1421]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">P. bilobatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFF1C1077CBDFAC6FBEBF3DD" authorityName="P. E. A. S. Camara" authorityYear="2010" baseAuthorityName="Bosch &amp; Sande Lac." box="[994,1138,1395,1421]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="glossoides">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFF1C1077CBDFAC6FBEBF3DD" box="[994,1138,1395,1421]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">P. glossoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFF1C1077BDEFAC6FA95F3DD" authorityName="W. R. Buck" authorityYear="1987" baseAuthorityName="Cardot" box="[1153,1292,1395,1421]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Phyllodon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="lingulatus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFF1C1077BDEFAC6FA95F3DD" box="[1153,1292,1395,1421]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">P. lingulatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFF1C1077A44FAC6FE44F3E2" authority="(Mitt.) J. T. Wynns (2020: 647)" authorityName="J. T. Wynns" authorityPageNumber="647" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Mitt." class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="laevifolius">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFF1C1077A44FAC6FA35F3DD" box="[1307,1452,1395,1421]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">P. laevifolius</emphasis>
(Mitt.) J.T. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB940F0FFF1C1077E59FA25FE44F3E2" author="Wynns, J. T." box="[262,477,1431,1458]" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" pagination="633 - 656" refId="ref9928" refString="Wynns, J. T. (2020) New names and new combinations for hypnalean mosses. The Bryologist 123 (4): 633 - 656. https: // doi. org / 10.1639 / 0007 - 2745 - 122.4.633" type="journal article" year="2020">Wynns (2020: 647)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFF1C1077D4CFA2AFC54F3E1" authority="(Bosch &amp; Sande Lac.) S. He" authorityName="S. He" baseAuthorityName="Bosch &amp; Sande Lac." box="[531,973,1431,1457]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="similans">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFF1C1077D4CFA2AFD12F3E1" box="[531,651,1431,1457]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">P. similans</emphasis>
(Bosch &amp; Sande Lac.) S. He
</taxonomicName>
in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB940F0FFF1C1077CB0FA25FA93F3E2" author="He, S. &amp; Nguyen, K. S." box="[1007,1290,1431,1458]" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" pagination="32 - 88" refId="ref8494" refString="He, S. &amp; Nguyen, K. S. (2012) New records and an updated checklist of the mosses of Vietnam. Tropical Bryology 34: 32 - 88. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / bde. 34.1.5" type="journal article" year="2012">He &amp; Nguyen (2012: 59)</bibRefCitation>
. In the present study, only one species 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFF1C1077ED7FA09FD8BF384" authorityName="W. R. Buck" authorityYear="1987" baseAuthorityName="Cardot" box="[392,530,1466,1492]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Phyllodon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="lingulatus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFF1C1077ED7FA09FD8BF384" box="[392,530,1466,1492]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">P. lingulatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is confirmed, whereas other four species records are interpreted as misidentification and should be excluded from moss flora of 
<collectingCountry id="F33F7D91FFF1C1077DDFFA6FFD5EF3A7" box="[640,711,1501,1527]" name="China" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">China</collectingCountry>
. For details, see the section “Species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C284682FFF1C1077BC7FA6FFAA4F3A7" authorityName="M. Fleischer (1923:" authorityYear="1351" box="[1176,1341,1501,1527]" class="Bryopsida" family="Hypnaceae" genus="Glossadelphus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="1" pageNumber="226" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B95CE113FFF1C1077BC7FA6FFAA4F3A7" box="[1176,1341,1501,1527]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">Glossadelphus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
excluded from moss flora of 
<collectingCountry id="F33F7D91FFF1C1077E3FF9B2FE3FF04A" box="[352,422,1536,1562]" name="China" pageId="1" pageNumber="226">China</collectingCountry>
” below.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
